					<description><![CDATA[<p>K1x Secures Major Capital to Expand AI Tax Infrastructure K1x has secured a $175 million growth investment round led by Sumeru Equity Partners. Edison Partners also participated in the transaction.</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/k1x-secures-175m-ai-tax-platform/" data-wpel-link="internal">K1x Secures $175 Million Growth Investment to Scale AI Tax Infrastructure</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
